        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 6 at 4:00PM MDT until June 6 at 4:30PM MDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>SVRMAF

The National Weather Service in Midland has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northeastern Lea County in southeastern New Mexico...

* Until 430 PM MDT.

* At 359 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Crossroads,
or 17 miles north of Tatum, moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage
to roofs, siding, and trees.

* Locations impacted include...
Crossroads.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

A Tornado Watch remains in effect until 1000 PM MDT for southeastern
New Mexico.</instruction>
